cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with camera localization in a known 3D scene using computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves regression tasks, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of Random Forests and Neural Networks also suggests that the paper could be relevant to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics).
